# Impeccable (https://github.com/pbakaus/impeccable/blob/main/.gitignore):
# track PRODUCT.md, DESIGN.md, and root DESIGN.json; keep live/cache/history local.
.impeccable/live/server.json
.impeccable/live/sessions/
.impeccable/live/annotations/
.impeccable/live/cache/
.impeccable/history/
.impeccable-live.json
.impeccable-live/
# Legacy per-project design context (pre-v3.1; teach migrates to PRODUCT.md)
.impeccable.md
# Sidecar lives at repo root (DESIGN.json); ignore harness mirror if present.
.impeccable/design.json

# Viewer cache (converted replay artifacts)
.viewer-cache/
*.json.ndjson
*.json.ndjson.idx
*.json.states.ndjson
*.json.states.ndjson.idx
